summary: An ordinance providing for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of 6th Avenue West, from West McGraw Street to East Ray Street as produced; West McGraw Street from 7th Avenue West to 3rd Avenue West; West Smith Street, from 7th Avenue West to 3rd Avenue West; and West Ray Street from 7th Avenue West to 6th Avenue South as produced, over and across certain lots, blocks and parcels of land.
